        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2425214601" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16437132660568170408">Possibly the worst zombie book in the entire world. The book is written in an extremely annoying style, consisting of a constant narration of what people said and did.</span>

